{"tid":1457622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入返機場做和理非，令黑警自打嘴巴","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:29:37.000Z","uid":5996,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd6bcddfd89da793d4301b8e62cc42effb25ae5","tid":1457622,"uid":5996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:58:25.000Z","msg":"首先睇下江永祥講咩：<br />\n<br />\n【網傳警方6時機場清場 】<br />\n【警方：「若示威者不做任何野，警方亦不會做任何野」】<br />\n網上有消息指，警方將會在機場進行驅散行動，江永祥回應指，上星期五、六、日示威者和平表達訴求，警方沒有干預，<span style=\"color: red;\">但若示威者暴力升級，警方將別無他選作適當介入</span>。<br />\n江永祥強調機場是重要設施，不容任何人作大肆破壞，指若示威者「不做任何野」，警方亦「不會做任何野」。<br />\n#香港電台 #港台電視31 #港台電視32 #十點半新聞天地 #香港警察 #機場<br />\n<br />\n而家一大班人離場，其實輿論上對我地不利<br />\n因為黑警可以話：「你睇，成班乖乖地聽警方勸喻離場咪冇事，幾和平，警方冇用任何暴力」<br />\n呢次完全係被撚狗咁撚<br />\n但江永祥上面highlight左果句帶出一個重點<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\">示威者和平表達訴求，警方沒有干預，但若示威者暴力升級，警方將別無他選作適當介入</span>」<br />\n換言之，只要響機場和理飛，黑警如果都照用武力驅散就係反口<br />\n輿論都有利我地好多！"},{"pid":"387a7e7b451c7bd6a05124e1fd9f29d1c455a5a5","tid":1457622,"uid":304306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:59:12.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻阻大家 我想推廣一下係葵芳散步GE方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n葵芳區漫步指南<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457449\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457449</a>"},{"pid":"19666d94fbb0fe6f1c5b82364d93b0df92010383","tid":1457622,"uid":5996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7120d22e8bb628cbad085791c1447dd4af30e1dd","tid":1457622,"uid":61882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:00:14.000Z","msg":"狗反口、撐大眼講大話係常識，係定律"},{"pid":"f20a5b5d4b80ceee2857ecb0be5f0eff34fab43e","tid":1457622,"uid":140738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:00:44.000Z","msg":"機場開24/7<br />\n<br />\n入機場本身係唔犯法<br />\n<br />\n唔好係到製造恐慌"},{"pid":"c4d5240fd67cc35a866dced24b4a0320c2bc0e86","tid":1457622,"uid":5996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7120d22e8bb628cbad085791c1447dd4af30e1dd","tid":1457622,"uid":61882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:00:14.000Z","msg":"狗反口、撐大眼講大話係常識，係定律"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:02:23.000Z","msg":"我知，但既然仲有航班降落，現場仲有手足，亦有唔少人返番去<br />\n大家一齊入機場唔止增援，仲有輿論效果"},{"pid":"f1bbe08bca8549e01ae2bc39aa05e845def937b7","tid":1457622,"uid":5996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f20a5b5d4b80ceee2857ecb0be5f0eff34fab43e","tid":1457622,"uid":140738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:00:44.000Z","msg":"機場開24/7<br />\n<br />\n入機場本身係唔犯法<br />\n<br />\n唔好係到製造恐慌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:03:02.000Z","msg":"係，大家一齊入返機場呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09bbc25d75c98fa5cc246415418efec9158339a","tid":1457622,"uid":103414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:17:53.000Z","msg":"準備入返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5b79d8f4b743bf93b29edc84b19b8ce4a5d0b0","tid":1457622,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:29:37.000Z","msg":"小心有25狗係入面成批攪事俾機會班狗清場"}]}